default New
default CTR regulations for England, Scotland and Wal
defaultes amount to just under 800 pages.
default&#xa0;
defaultConclusionsdefault1.34
default&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultAs time passes, the scale and nature of the impact of recent reforms to support with housing costs are becoming more apparent. 
defaultIt is important that proper account is taken of these impacts, and that policy ch
defaultanges to offset the most serious are considered so that the UK’s ability to meet housing needs does not face further barriers.
default1.35
default&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultUniversal credit is still on the horizon but lessons from the demonstration projects and the reforms already implemented are valu
defaultable and must be used in forthcoming work to get this beleaguered policy to achieve its valuable original aims.  
